I guess I'll do a brief intro into Coven.
Coven, unlike wolves, do not have a constant killing role.
We are more focused on creating havoc in the village.
For example, my role disrupts the voting system of the village via 2 powers that I can use every night.
Shroud - I prevent a player from getting lynched
Silence - I prevent a player's vote from counting.
Effectively, a silenced player's vote = jackshit. They can't make a decisive vote to lynch for the day,
